    topic: "Neurology",
    subtopic: "Huntington Disease Genetic Testing in Minors",
    stem: `Mother of an 8-year-old girl has brought her for genetic testing for Huntington disease because the father has been recently diagnosed with the disease. She knows that the disease can have been passed to her daughter as well and she is very worries about this issue. Which one of the following is the most appropriate action in this situation?`,
