    topic: "Neurology",
    subtopic: "Dialysis non-compliance management",
    stem: `A 65-year-old man, who is on chronic hemodialysis every other day due to chronic renal failure, presents to the emergency department with generalised weakness and dyspnea. He is non-compliant with his dialysis sessions and had his last session five days ago. Which of the following would be the most appropriate next action?`,
