    topic: "Neurology",
    subtopic: "Testicular cancer diagnosis and tumour markers",
    stem: `A 20-year-old male patient presents to your clinic with painless scrotal swelling. Ultrasound shows a solid mass in the left testis. Which one of the following is the next best step in management?`,
